To use Tweet Me Tunes:

(1) Sign in to Twitter.
(2) Follow @tweetmetunes.
(3) Once @tweetmetunes is following you back, DM it the name of an artist (and optionally a track). You can use the form at http://tweetmetunes.electrovert.net to format your message.
(4) You will receive a recommendation as an @reply.

You don't need to (nor will you be able to) execute the bot yourself.